roach minima limits) and 2 others. Changed since last run: Shirak (LWN/UDSG), Keflavik (KEF/BIKF), Almaty (ALA/UAAA), Varna (VAR/LBWN), Cristiano Ronaldo (FNC/LPMA), Zvartnots (EVN/UDYZ), Bordeaux–Mérignac (BOD/LFBD), Paris-Orly (ORY/LFPO), David the Builder Kutaisi (KUT/UGKO), Francisco de Sá Carneiro (OPO/LPPR) and 2 others.",
